{"tid":1099630,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(WTF)勇者鬥惡龍DQCG電影版,因為製作方認為鳥山明的畫風不適歐美市場,而改為迪士尼畫風","createTime":"2019-04-10T01:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T08:29:35.000Z","uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"53e06ca9db6e36aade47386047f4cfd999be9f84","tid":1099630,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PNPctbh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPNPctbh.jpg&h=4eaa7fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n製作方認為,DQ一直以來只在日本國內大賣,在歐美賣得唔好，<br />\n是因為鳥山明的畫風不適合厚重的故事,所以只在日本國內受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n所以他們改成類似迪士尼的畫風,想開拓海外市場,即使一部分日本fans唔鍾意都要冒險。<br />\n對此DQ日本fans的態度,以前靠我地賺錢現在想踢開我地,沒有鳥山明你還畫DQ?<br />\n你地遊戲做差咪怪鳥山明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sabukaru.net/?p=52605\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsabukaru.net%2F%3Fp%3D52605&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIlT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=dd1aa39e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sabukaru.net/?p=52605</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nドラゴンクエスト ユア・ストーリー 勇者鬥惡龍CG電影預告<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1091459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1091459</a>"},{"pid":"73a7a238ccbef4aa3bafba4a0fbb161a6a470b59","tid":1099630,"uid":31219,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:02:23.000Z","msg":"鳥山明上咗神枱都唔適合？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c2f6a9cb3b5d86f58dbb4bda810becb602efec","tid":1099630,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"73a7a238ccbef4aa3bafba4a0fbb161a6a470b59","tid":1099630,"uid":31219,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:02:23.000Z","msg":"鳥山明上咗神枱都唔適合？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:07:44.000Z","msg":"所以咪wtf"},{"pid":"7c1a08adb82d102c4a9fc0697ff2499e3eb11de2","tid":1099630,"uid":31219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"